headline: Starbucks CEO talks rising coffee prices and tariffs
summary: Coffee prices (KC=F) have risen more than 20% over the past year. President Trump's tariffs could cause them to climb even higher. Starbucks (SBUX) CEO Brian Niccol explains how the company prepares for higher prices and if it means you will have to start paying more for your morning cup.
